@startuml
!theme mono

title PAYMENT 서비스 - Entity Relationship Diagram

!define TABLE(name,desc) class name as "desc" << (T,#FFAAAA) >>
!define PK(x) <b>x</b>
!define FK(x) <i>x</i>
!define UNIQUE(x) <u>x</u>

TABLE(subscriptions, "SUBSCRIPTIONS\n(구독)") {
    PK(id: VARCHAR(36))
    --
    UNIQUE(user_id: VARCHAR(36)) NOT NULL
    plan_id: VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
    tier: VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
    status: VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
    provider: VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
    transaction_id: VARCHAR(200)
    started_at: TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL
    expires_at: TIMESTAMPTZ
    --
    created_at: TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL
    updated_at: TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL
}

TABLE(payment_records, "PAYMENT_RECORDS\n(결제 이력 - insert-only)") {
    PK(id: VARCHAR(36))
    --
    FK(subscription_id: VARCHAR(36)) NOT NULL
    user_id: VARCHAR(36) NOT NULL
    UNIQUE(transaction_id: VARCHAR(200)) NOT NULL
    amount: INTEGER NOT NULL
    currency: VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL
    provider: VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
    --
    created_at: TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL
}

' 관계 정의
subscriptions ||--o{ payment_records : "has payment records"

note top of subscriptions
  <b>Indexes:</b>
  • idx_subscriptions_user_id (user_id) UNIQUE
  • idx_subscriptions_status (status)
  • idx_subscriptions_expires_at (expires_at)

  <b>Check Constraints:</b>
  • tier IN ('FREE', 'TRIP_PASS', 'PRO')
  • status IN ('ACTIVE', 'CANCELLED', 'CANCELLING')
  • provider IN ('APPLE', 'GOOGLE')

  <b>External Reference (no FK):</b>
  • user_id → AUTH.users.id

  <b>Design Note:</b>
  • user_id UNIQUE: 사용자당 1개 활성 구독
  • SubscriptionPlan은 코드/설정 파일로 관리
end note

note bottom of payment_records
  <b>Indexes:</b>
  • idx_payment_records_user_id (user_id)
  • idx_payment_records_subscription_id (subscription_id)
  • idx_payment_records_transaction_id UNIQUE
  • idx_payment_records_created_at (created_at)

  <b>Foreign Key Actions:</b>
  • subscription_id: ON DELETE RESTRICT

  <b>Check Constraints:</b>
  • amount > 0

  <b>Design Note:</b>
  • Insert-only (불변 레코드)
  • transaction_id UNIQUE: 중복 결제 방지
end note

legend right
  <b>Redis Cache (DB 7):</b>
  pay:subscription:{userId}    TTL 5분

  <b>External Services:</b>
  IapVerificationClient (Apple/Google IAP)
  AuthServiceClient (tier 업데이트 동기 호출)

  <b>Legend:</b>
  PK = Primary Key
  FK = Foreign Key
  UNIQUE = Unique Constraint
end legend

@enduml
